{"tid":1496812,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[香 港 要 人！！！]我地一齊組成香港之路","createTime":"2019-08-22T16:30:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T06:09:27.000Z","uid":40431,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"90f3dbaded4c546889f9bab7bde639d6b3d0f1a4","tid":1496812,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:30:13.000Z","msg":"1989年8月23日嘅波羅的海&mdash;愛沙尼亞、拉脫維亞、立陶宛三個小國組成咗一條由塔林經過里加，去到維爾紐斯，總共675.5公里嘅波羅的海之路。呢條路令當時同樣渴望自由嘅200萬人connected，由小朋友到老人，三小國嘅<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">半數人口</span>都走上街頭，團結一致地對抗蘇聯嘅野心。短短15分鐘就訂下咗後來堅定不移嘅步伐。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XZ6xDoF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXZ6xDoF.jpg&h=36b532b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在30年後嘅聽日，我地要喺香港重現佢哋當年以和平姿態，為自由而奮鬥嘅精神，一齊展現對中共極權嘅反抗。呢個活動已經引起咗國際社會嘅廣泛關注，波羅的海嘅傳媒甚至特登派咗記者嚟香港採訪。如果我地香港人連當年波羅的海三小國嘅水平都做唔到，<strong>我地唔單止冇資格去話五大訴求，缺一不可，甚至會成為國際笑話。</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bJ7T7hm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbJ7T7hm.jpg&h=3173766b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cKXABaH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcKXABaH.jpg&h=f9d841dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n30年前，三小國有200萬位前人已經做過一次，30年後，自命高汁嘅香港人難道連拖起手組條人鏈都做唔到？我地要用香港人嘅方式，抗爭者嘅集體智慧，去重現、甚至超越當年嘅人鏈。用影像同埋事實，話俾世界所有擁有自由意志嘅人，以及世界各地嘅媒體聽：香港人擁抱自由嘅決心，比任何國度嘅人更強。我地要重現，甚至去超越當年既壯舉，以行動做一次世界性嘅宣示。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019年8月23日晚，我地要在香港天空之下，夜景街道之間，拖住擁抱自由嘅手足，刻下歷史最輝煌嘅一頁！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pW43K4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpW43K4b.jpg&h=eac6dc9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！！！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！！！</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人，聽晚，香港見。</span></span>"},{"pid":"8671aa9653f97b995bffc6bb33d4bee0216431b8","tid":1496812,"uid":259987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:31:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"de4601fd16c3342b8e764f95405d9487ca23583a","tid":1496812,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:31:54.000Z","msg":"823人鏈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cdfd2b6ba4971bac9ef15fa149bc48fc7c4ff43","tid":1496812,"uid":259987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:32:14.000Z","msg":"puuuush"},{"pid":"524b193234905bd8393e739d2a1cc1b6745084a0","tid":1496812,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:32:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54a7f48014aefaab79c162ba50ab543264de0a37","tid":1496812,"uid":24465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:33:16.000Z","msg":"一句講晒 9月1 - 2 機場見<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1496431\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1496431</a>"},{"pid":"4282ab0bae10e6282dcb941b3eb954f38889755d","tid":1496812,"uid":259987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:33:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f6b6195a9397a4a8979689c58bb600242191b164","tid":1496812,"uid":6630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:34:31.000Z","msg":"今日和你拖"},{"pid":"4c7896bb99d15992aad81e072038dcc595be46f2","tid":1496812,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:35:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd4344d297e070c0dd