 />\n<br />\n823 823 823 紅藍綠三線和你牽<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1495732\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1495732</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eV7XPEp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeV7XPEp.jpg&h=d7220f4a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ULw9FL5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FULw9FL5.jpg&h=b4fbfe77&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dXB9FL8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdXB9FL8.jpg&h=e113c33c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bX8W5cQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbX8W5cQ.jpg&h=5a9c9458&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行動post好難推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8c453ccb244aee10cf278f6d70df2e16ddc0a43","tid":1496812,"uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90f3dbaded4c546889f9bab7bde639d6b3d0f1a4","tid":1496812,"uid":40431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:30:13.000Z","msg":"1989年8月23日嘅波羅的海&mdash;愛沙尼亞、拉脫維亞、立陶宛三個小國組成咗一條由塔林經過里加，去到維爾紐斯，總共675.5公里嘅波羅的海之路。呢條路令當時同樣渴望自由嘅200萬人connected，由小朋友到老人，三小國嘅<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">半數人口</span>都走上街頭，團結一致地對抗蘇聯嘅野心。短短15分鐘就訂下咗後來堅定不移嘅步伐。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XZ6xDoF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXZ6xDoF.jpg&h=36b532b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在30年後嘅聽日，我地要喺香港重現佢哋當年以和平姿態，為自由而奮鬥嘅精神，一齊展現對中共極權嘅反抗。呢個活動已經引起咗國際社會嘅廣泛關注，波羅的海嘅傳媒甚至特登派咗記者嚟香港採訪。如果我地香港人連當年波羅的海三小國嘅水平都做唔到，<strong>我地唔單止冇資格去話五大訴求，缺一不可，甚至會成為國際笑話。</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bJ7T7hm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbJ7T7hm.jpg&h=3173766b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cKXABaH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcKXABaH.jpg&h=f9d841dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n30年前，三小國有200萬位前人已經做過一次，30年後，自命高汁嘅香港人難道連拖起手組條人鏈都做唔到？我地要用香港人嘅方式，抗爭者嘅集體智慧，去重現、甚至超越當年嘅人鏈。用影像同埋事實，話俾世界所有擁有自由意志嘅人，以及世界各地嘅媒體聽：香港人擁抱自由嘅決心，比任何國度嘅人更強。我地要重現，甚至去超越當年既壯舉，以行動做一次世界性嘅宣示。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019年8月23日晚，我地要在香港天空之下，夜景街道之間，拖住擁抱自由嘅手足，刻下歷史最輝煌嘅一頁！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pW43K4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpW43K4b.jpg&h=eac6dc9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！！！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！！！</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人，聽晚，香港見。</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:50:05.000Z","msg":"幾多點呀？"},{"pid":"a5428ad6ff1d16be9b15c1cbd29257c23dc46823","tid":1496812,"uid":181939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:53:34.000Z","msg":"823"},{"pid":"c85119ae8fb0b84d1ba2526ecd9aef1cdce2a562","tid":1496812,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:53:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd87581d438382d12413037c5f512ee21e2773c","tid":1496812,"uid":195540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:54:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"afe4eb2f6bd49e7a161a7c0e94e095606779c337","tid":1496812,"uid":43804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:55:26.000Z","msg":"真！！！<br />\n人哋Baltic States都咁關注，<br />\n我哋至少點都要畀到壯觀嘅畫面出嚟！"},{"pid":"12beec273e61ce9d49a7672b8b6e4e34efdfcff3","tid":1496812,"uid":133728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:55:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c36f941334dc73de28542eb7aa833750cc620175","tid":1496812,"uid":3448